WEBVTT

00:00:07.825 --> 00:00:11.562
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.812 --> 00:00:15.130
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.412 --> 00:00:23.912
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.675 --> 00:00:27.062
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.162 --> 00:00:29.200
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.312 --> 00:00:32.500
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:40.340
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.425 --> 00:00:42.837
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.887 --> 00:00:44.737
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.887 --> 00:00:48.400
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.550 --> 00:00:53.825
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.937 --> 00:00:56.237
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.737 --> 00:00:58.737
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.975 --> 00:00:59.720
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.720 --> 00:01:00.987
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.812 --> 00:01:03.400
=Episode 4=

00:01:04.159 --> 00:01:05.079
Official Gu,

00:01:05.959 --> 00:01:08.439
Huanyue House
has stood in the Capital for many years.

00:01:08.959 --> 00:01:10.280
Its roots run deep.

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:11.879
If you cross Huanyue House,

00:01:11.879 --> 00:01:12.799
the consequences,

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:14.799
surely you understand.

00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:19.239
Have you considered

00:01:20.079 --> 00:01:21.640
what it would cost

00:01:23.799 --> 00:01:25.200
to oppose me?

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.599
It seems

00:01:28.239 --> 00:01:30.719
you come with confident.

00:01:30.719 --> 00:01:32.439
Who told you I was here to investigate?

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:38.719
I came here for the ladies.

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:41.879
Young Master Gu.

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:45.599
The lady has been arranged for you.

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:46.879
This way, please.

00:02:32.479 --> 00:02:33.280
Official Gu,

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:34.639
please have some tea.

00:02:38.879 --> 00:02:39.479
Rise.

00:02:40.439 --> 00:02:41.439
There is no one else here.

00:02:41.439 --> 00:02:42.479
No.

00:02:43.240 --> 00:02:44.039
Don't touch me.

00:02:50.840 --> 00:02:52.039
What did they do to you?

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:02.879
Your nails...

00:03:05.599 --> 00:03:07.240
Was it Shangguan Yu or Zhou Zihua?

00:03:08.719 --> 00:03:09.800
Stop asking.

00:03:10.512 --> 00:03:11.312
Official Gu,

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:12.840
from now on,

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:14.159
please do not come see me again.

00:03:28.199 --> 00:03:30.199
You truly are of no use.

00:03:42.479 --> 00:03:43.520
Do not be nervous.

00:03:43.879 --> 00:03:45.400
It is only something for the pain.

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:47.319
Careful. Walls have ears.

00:04:19.079 --> 00:04:19.720
Sir,

00:04:20.240 --> 00:04:21.720
just as we expected,

00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:23.839
the two of them
have completely fallen out.

00:04:27.862 --> 00:04:30.221
That Yidianhong was well taught indeed.

00:04:30.759 --> 00:04:32.240
As for Song Zhiyun,

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:33.920
she knows when to yield.

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:35.439
What is the righteous path,

00:04:35.439 --> 00:04:36.920
and what is a dead end,

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:40.040
she understands perfectly.

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:43.079
I underestimated

00:04:43.079 --> 00:04:45.079
how dangerous Huanyue House truly is.

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:48.839
Wei Cheng.

00:04:50.240 --> 00:04:52.519
Before the Flower Festival, send her away.

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:56.000
But we no longer have
any informants in Huanyue House.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.600
She is full of flaws now.

00:05:01.079 --> 00:05:02.680
She is nothing but a discarded piece.

00:05:03.519 --> 00:05:04.800
Send her as far away as possible.

00:05:05.519 --> 00:05:06.879
I do not wish to see her again.

00:05:08.925 --> 00:05:09.725
Official...

00:05:13.120 --> 00:05:14.680
Have you grown fond of her?

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.120
Yes, you have.

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:25.959
In a few days,

00:05:25.959 --> 00:05:27.199
it will be the Flower Festival.

00:05:27.637 --> 00:05:30.000
This is your chance
to rise above the rest.

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:32.519
If you can become the leading courtesan,

00:05:32.519 --> 00:05:35.037
you will gain entry to that place.

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:36.600
There,

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:39.399
the powerful and noble gather.

00:05:40.199 --> 00:05:41.879
If one of them favors you,

00:05:41.879 --> 00:05:43.879
you may shed your low status

00:05:44.519 --> 00:05:46.079
and marry into a great family.

00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:47.959
(Jade Grove and Fair Trees)
Do not forget,

00:05:47.959 --> 00:05:50.600
Ruyu, the first courtesan queen
of Huanyue House,

00:05:50.759 --> 00:05:52.759
married into a marquis' household.

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:54.319
I heard that last year,

00:05:54.319 --> 00:05:56.000
she was granted an official title.

00:05:56.319 --> 00:05:58.040
Whether you change your fate

00:05:58.519 --> 00:06:00.079
is up to you.

00:06:01.319 --> 00:06:04.000
You would do better not
to waste your effort.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:07.079
This year's courtesan queen
of Huanyue House

00:06:07.079 --> 00:06:08.560
will be mine.

00:06:09.480 --> 00:06:10.759
The next titled lady

00:06:10.759 --> 00:06:12.160
will be me, Su Wanniang.

00:06:12.519 --> 00:06:14.319
As for you... Hmph.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.420
(Low-ranking maids are not allowed
to attend the Flower Festival.)

00:06:18.839 --> 00:06:20.079
(I need to find a way in.)

00:06:20.520 --> 00:06:22.840
(Only then can I work
with Gu Chengye from the inside and out)

00:06:22.840 --> 00:06:24.120
(and capture the painter.)

00:06:26.312 --> 00:06:29.275
(Jade Grove and Fair Trees.
On the day of the Flower Festival)

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:32.920
My face.

00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:34.279
- My face.
- Su Wanniang,

00:06:34.279 --> 00:06:36.175
you are about to go on.
What are you waiting for?

00:06:38.879 --> 00:06:39.800
Your face...

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:41.319
What happened to your face?

00:06:41.879 --> 00:06:43.720
It is only a rash
from some willow fluff.

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:45.319
A little touch-up and I can go on stage.

00:06:45.319 --> 00:06:46.879
The guests are
all powerful and affluent.

00:06:47.325 --> 00:06:48.818
I will not let you ruin our reputation.

00:06:49.439 --> 00:06:50.240
Take it as

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:51.279
fate not favoring you.

00:06:54.240 --> 00:06:55.839
Madam Du, Madam Du,

00:06:55.839 --> 00:06:58.199
I beg you,
please let me go on, Madam Du.

00:07:00.279 --> 00:07:01.160
Madam Du!

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:07.680
Su Wanniang.

00:07:11.879 --> 00:07:12.920
Song Zhiyun.

00:07:14.879 --> 00:07:15.680
Song Zhiyun.

00:07:16.519 --> 00:07:17.240
Was it you?

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:18.839
Was it you who did this to me?

00:07:19.079 --> 00:07:20.712
Yes, it was me.

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.720
I added a little nettle

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:23.839
to your face powder.

00:07:25.839 --> 00:07:26.987
You vicious woman.

00:07:30.319 --> 00:07:31.600
What exactly do you want?

00:07:32.279 --> 00:07:33.079
Su Wanniang,

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:35.319
you have two options now.

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:39.040
First, you can
keep arguing with me here.

00:07:39.040 --> 00:07:40.439
But I'm afraid

00:07:40.439 --> 00:07:42.240
you will end up just like I did,

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:43.839
the laughingstock of Huanyue House.

00:07:46.279 --> 00:07:48.519
Second, let me be your makeup attendant.

00:07:49.240 --> 00:07:50.560
If the two of us work together,

00:07:51.199 --> 00:07:52.439
I have a way

00:07:52.439 --> 00:07:53.912
to help you win the courtesan crown.

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:12.480
Su Wanniang. It is Su Wanniang.

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:39.600
This is the Hundred Flowers Dance.

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:43.440
At the Flower Festival,
we admire fresh blossoms and new dances.

00:08:43.937 --> 00:08:46.240
It truly does justice to the spring.

00:08:59.937 --> 00:09:01.858
Excellent. Excellent.

00:09:02.860 --> 00:09:04.320
Such beauty stirs pity and admiration.

00:09:04.919 --> 00:09:06.120
Compared with Liu Ruyan,

00:09:06.120 --> 00:09:07.159
she surpasses her.

00:09:07.679 --> 00:09:08.559
Indeed.

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:11.159
Did you not say

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:14.000
that Su Wanniang's face was ruined?

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:16.919
I heard

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:19.320
Song Zhiyun helped her.

00:09:20.862 --> 00:09:22.541
Song Zhiyun.

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:29.879
What a beautiful young lady.

00:09:33.825 --> 00:09:35.675
(Liu Jinxi. Su Wanniang.)

00:09:52.919 --> 00:09:53.840
Return to your room.

00:10:09.919 --> 00:10:10.799
Song Zhiyun?

00:10:11.240 --> 00:10:12.320
What are you doing here?

00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:13.440
Did I not tell you to leave?

00:10:14.360 --> 00:10:17.399
Second-floor private room.
A pot of Nverhong.

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.240
There is no time to explain.

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.039
What are you waiting for? Hide him.

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:38.879
Song Zhiyun.

00:10:39.159 --> 00:10:40.120
What are you trying to...

00:10:40.120 --> 00:10:41.320
Hush. Do not speak.

00:10:46.039 --> 00:10:46.840
Honored guest,

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:48.960
this is a complimentary pot
of our finest Nu'erhong.

00:10:52.550 --> 00:10:55.837
♪Even if I drift
within a darkened whirl♪

00:10:56.437 --> 00:11:00.325
♪Kindred souls
meet the light and become one♪

00:11:00.487 --> 00:11:07.987
♪So many chapters,
every wound remembered♪

00:11:08.225 --> 00:11:11.712
♪Back where we once stood,
the blossoms still remain♪

00:11:12.025 --> 00:11:15.337
♪The night runs deep like watching eyes♪

00:11:15.475 --> 00:11:16.725
♪Wave after wave of sorrow♪

00:11:16.759 --> 00:11:17.519
Sir,

00:11:17.519 --> 00:11:18.519
here's your wine.

00:11:20.240 --> 00:11:21.000
My apologies

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:22.240
for the interruption.

00:11:24.612 --> 00:11:27.112
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:11:27.287 --> 00:11:29.287
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:11:29.425 --> 00:11:32.725
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:11:33.075 --> 00:11:38.360
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:11:38.360 --> 00:11:40.759
How much longer will you keep it buried?

00:11:40.837 --> 00:11:42.800
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:11:42.835 --> 00:11:44.755
♪For all our days to come♪

00:11:44.755 --> 00:11:47.100
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪